  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      comparing conservative management versus interventional management in hemodynamically stable&#xD;
      paediatric patient with blunt renal trauma, evidence suggests that there is a reduced rate of&#xD;
      renal loss and blood transfusion in patients managed conservatively.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
